 o plan and install their thesis work. The exhibition features graduate st
 udent work from a variety of studio areas: ceramics\, digital arts\, fibe
 rs\, graphic design\, metalsmithing &amp\; jewelry design\, painting\, ph
 otography\, printmaking\, and sculpture.  &#160\;MFA Group 1 ArtistsKenne
