 en couture by graduating fashion design students regularly draws a standi
 ng-room-only audience in Alumni Hall. Every aspect of this lively annual 
 extravaganza is produced by students as a professional development opport
 unity. Doors open at 6:30pm.This event is free and open to the public.  P
 roduced by the Retail Studies Organization and fashion design students\, 
 in partnership with the Eskenazi School Center for Innovative Merchandisi
 ng\, The Paul Mitchell School\, and an anonymous donor.
