 ontrast="auto">\, on Friday\, April 17\, 4:00 pm-6:00 pm EDT. The event w
 ill begin with remarks by Katie Chattin\, Director of the IU Public Art a
 nd Cultural Heritage Collection\, and Paula Katz\, Senior Curator of Art 
