BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:IU Eskenazi School of Art, Architecture + Design
DTSTART:20260620T170000Z
DTEND:20260620T180000Z
LOCATION:SIDNEY AND LOIS ESKENAZI MUSEUM OF ART - Room Number: check in w
 ith Guest Services at the information desk on the first floor
SUMMARY:Relaxing with Landscapes
DESCRIPTION:Cool down your body while heating up your mind as we discuss 
 what we see as a group\, helping each other discover details we might oth
 erwise miss in a quick visit through the galleries.    About Your Guide  
 Dr. TammyJo Eckhart is an ancient historian who has enjoyed being part of
  the Eskenazi Guide Program since 2009. She was the 2025 recipient of the
  Patricia and Joel Meier Guide Award from that program. She looks forward
  to sitting with you and really spending time with these wonderful landsc
 apes.    Know Before You Go  Space is available for the first 12 people t
 o check in with Guest Services on the day. Drop by the information desk o
 n the first floor of the museum when you arrive.A small handbag may be ca
 rried at your side. Backpacks and large bags will need to be stored befor
 e touring. Learn more aboutmuseum guidelines.If you park in the IMU parki
 ng lot\, Guest Services can validate your parking voucher for a discount.
 Read aboutwhere to find us and where to park\,
